  "local_port": 43740,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some good resources to learn web scraping with Python?",
  "response": "Learning web scraping with Python can be very rewarding, and there are numerous resources available to help you get started. Here are some highly recommended ones:\n\n### Books\n1. **\"Web Scraping with Python\" by Ryan Mitchell**: This book is a comprehensive guide to web scraping using Python. It covers BeautifulSoup, Selenium, and other tools.\n\n### Online Courses\n2. **Coursera**: \n   - [Web Scraping with Python](https://www.coursera.org/learn/web-scraping) by the University of Michigan.\n3. **Udemy**:\n   - [Python Web Scraping & Crawling](https://www.udemy.com/course/python-web-scraping-crawling/)\n4. **Pluralsight**:\n   - [Web Scraping in Python](https://www.pluralsight.com/courses/web-scraping-python)\n\n### Tutorials\n5. **Real Python**:\n   - [Web Scraping with Beautiful Soup and Python](https://realpython.com/beautiful-soup-web-scraper-python/)\n6. **DataCamp**:\n   - [Web Scraping with Python](https://www.datacamp.com/community/tutorials/tutorial-python-web-scraping)\n7. **ScrapingBee Blog**:\n   - [Ultimate Guide to Web Scraping with Python](https://www.scrapingbee.com/blog/web-scraping-python/)\n\n### Documentation\n8. **BeautifulSoup**: \n   - [BeautifulSoup Documentation](https://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/bs4/doc/)\n9. **Scrapy**:\n   - [Scrapy Documentation](https://docs.scrapy.org/en/latest/)\n10. **Selenium**:\n    - [Selenium Documentation](https://selenium-python.readthedocs.io/)\n\n### GitHub Repositories\n11. **Awesome Web Scraping**:\n    - [Awesome Web Scraping GitHub Repository](https://github.com/lorien/awesome-web-scraping)\n\n### Blogs and Articles\n12. **Towards Data Science**:\n    - [Web Scraping with Python: Step by Step Guide](https://towardsdatascience.com/web-scraping-python-tutorial-web-scraping-steps-with-python-6d7a1a8b5e2e)\n13. **Medium**:\n    - Search for web scraping tutorials on Medium for various articles and guides.\n\n### YouTube Channels\n14. **Programming with Mosh**:\n    - [Web Scraping with Python - BeautifulSoup Tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ng2o98k983k)\n15. **Corey Schafer**:\n    - [Web Scraping with Python](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ng2o98k983k)\n\n### Practice Platforms\n16. **Kaggle**:\n    - Participate in web scraping competitions and explore datasets that require scraping.\n\n### Tools to Explore\n- **BeautifulSoup**: A library for parsing HTML and XML documents.\n- **Scrapy**: An open-source web crawling framework.\n- **Selenium**: A tool for automating web browsers, useful for dynamic content.\n\nRemember to always respect the terms of service of websites you scrape and ensure you are compliant with legal and ethical guidelines.",
